trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle"></xref> objects in the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataGrid"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Reprezentuje kolekcję <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle"> </xref> obiekty w <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataGrid"> </xref> formantu.

trans-unit.source: The GridTableStylesCollection contains <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle> objects that allows the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGrid> control to display a customized grid style for each <xref:System.Data.DataTable> in a <xref:System.Data.DataSet>.
trans-unit.target: GridTableStylesCollection zawiera <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle>obiekty, które umożliwia <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGrid>formantu, aby wyświetlić styl dostosowane siatki dla każdego <xref:System.Data.DataTable> <xref:System.Data.DataSet>.</xref:System.Data.DataSet> </xref:System.Data.DataTable> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGrid> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle>

trans-unit.source: On the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGrid> control, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGrid.TableStyles%2A> property returns the GridTableStylesCollection.
By default, the GridTableStylesCollection does not contain any <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle> objects.
Instead, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGrid> displays each table using default settings for color, width, and formatting.
trans-unit.target: Zamiast tego <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGrid>Wyświetla każdej tabeli przy użyciu ustawień domyślnych kolor, szerokość i formatowanie.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGrid>

trans-unit.source: All columns of each table are displayed.
trans-unit.target: Wyświetlane są wszystkie kolumny w każdej tabeli.

trans-unit.source: When a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle> is added to the collection, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGrid> uses the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle.MappingName%2A> to determine which object supplies the data for the grid.
trans-unit.target: Gdy <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle>zostanie dodany do kolekcji, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGrid>używa <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle.MappingName%2A>ustalenie obiektu, który dostarcza dane w siatce.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle.MappingName%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGrid> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle>

trans-unit.source: For example, if the data source is a <xref:System.Data.DataSet> that contains three <xref:System.Data.DataTable> objects, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle.MappingName%2A> must match the <xref:System.Data.DataTable.TableName%2A> of one of the objects.
trans-unit.target: Na przykład, jeśli źródło danych jest <xref:System.Data.DataSet>zawiera trzy <xref:System.Data.DataTable>obiektów, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle.MappingName%2A>musi odpowiadać <xref:System.Data.DataTable.TableName%2A>z jednego z tych obiektów.</xref:System.Data.DataTable.TableName%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle.MappingName%2A> </xref:System.Data.DataTable> </xref:System.Data.DataSet>

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle.MappingName%2A> does not match any of the <xref:System.Data.DataTable.TableName%2A> values, the default settings will be used to display data for each table, and the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle> settings will be ignored.
trans-unit.target: Jeśli <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle.MappingName%2A>nie pasuje do żadnego z <xref:System.Data.DataTable.TableName%2A>wartości, domyślne ustawienia będą stosowane do wyświetlania danych dla każdej tabeli i <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle>Ustawienia zostaną zignorowane.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle> </xref:System.Data.DataTable.TableName%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle.MappingName%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!CAUTION] > Always create <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridColumnStyle> objects and add them to the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.GridColumnStylesCollection> before adding <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle> objects to the GridTableStylesCollection.
trans-unit.target: > [!CAUTION] > Zawsze twórz <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridColumnStyle>obiekty i dodaj je do <xref:System.Windows.Forms.GridColumnStylesCollection>przed dodaniem <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle>obiektów GridTableStylesCollection.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.GridColumnStylesCollection> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridColumnStyle>

trans-unit.source: When you add an empty <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle> with a valid <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle.MappingName%2A> value to the collection, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridColumnStyle> objects are automatically generated for you.
trans-unit.target: Po dodaniu pustą <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle>z prawidłowym <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle.MappingName%2A>wartości do kolekcji, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridColumnStyle>obiekty są generowane automatycznie.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridColumnStyle> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle.MappingName%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle>

trans-unit.source: Consequently, an exception will be thrown if you try to add new <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridColumnStyle> objects with duplicate <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle.MappingName%2A> values to the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.GridColumnStylesCollection>.
trans-unit.target: W związku z tym zostanie wygenerowany wyjątek przy próbie dodania nowych <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridColumnStyle>obiektów ze zduplikowanymi <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle.MappingName%2A>wartościami do <xref:System.Windows.Forms.GridColumnStylesCollection>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.GridColumnStylesCollection> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridTableStyle.MappingName%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridColumnStyle>

trans-unit.source: Alternatively, clear the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.GridColumnStylesCollection> using the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.GridColumnStylesCollection.Clear%2A> method.
